    <item>
      <title>中国经济仅靠一个引擎继续滑行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/world-economy-latest-china-s-economy-is-still-flying-on-just-one-engine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年中国经济依靠工业生产保持增长，未来一周的数据将提供线索，表明这种支撑力度还能有多大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-03/world-economy-latest-china-s-economy-is-still-flying-on-just-one-engine</guid>
